62 concurrent with that of the circuit court in cases originally
63 filed in the Probate Court of Blount County if the judge of
64 probate is licensed to practice law in the State of Alabama.
65 Proposed by Act ____."
66 This description shall be followed by the following
67 language:
68 "Yes( ) No( )."
69 Section 3. The proposed amendment shall become valid as
70 part of the Constitution of Alabama of 2022, when approved by
71 a majority of the qualified electors voting thereon.
